The '''Baobab Work Placement Bureau''' was a division of the [[Baobab Archives]]. Run by the [[Baobab family]], the bureau helped beings of many species obtain successful occupations throughout [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]]. Under the direction of [[Ebenn Q3 Baobab/Legends|Ebenn Q3 Baobab]], the Work Placement Bureau not only helped many [[Wookiee/Legends|Wookiees]] find jobs in the business sector, but held evening classes in numerous languages and pushed for equal-employment standards for all species.

